<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin: 30px 40px;
      color: #000;
    }
    .dual-header {
      text-align: center;
      border: 3px double #000;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .dual-header h1 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0 0 5px 0;
    }
    .dual-header .hindi {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 3px 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .tender-box {
      background: #fffacd;
      border: 2px solid #ffa500;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .tender-box .tender-no {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ff6600;
    }
    .info-section {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-section h3 {
      background: #4a4a4a;
      color: white;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin: 15px 0 8px 0;
    }
    .bilingual-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 6px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
    }
    .label-en {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #000;
    }
    .label-hi {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .govt-seal {
      position: fixed;
      top: 50px;
      right: 50px;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border: 2px solid #ff6600;
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.2;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="govt-seal">भारत सरकार<br>Govt of India</div>
  
  <div class="dual-header">
    <h1>{{organisation}}</h1>
    <div class="hindi">निविदा सूचना / TENDER NOTICE</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tender-box">
    <div class="tender-no">Tender No. / निविदा संख्या: {{tender_id}}</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 10px;">{{title}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>TENDER INFORMATION / निविदा जानकारी</h3>
    
    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Publication Date</div>
        <div class="label-hi">प्रकाशन तिथि</div>
      </div>
      <div>{{publish_date}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Bid Submission Deadline</div>
        <div class="label-hi">बोली जमा करने की अंतिम तिथि</div>
      </div>
      <div>{{due_date}} (2:00 PM IST)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Estimated Value</div>
        <div class="label-hi">अनुमानित मूल्य</div>
      </div>
      <div>₹ {{formatCurrency estimated_cost_inr}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Material Category</div>
        <div class="label-hi">सामग्री श्रेणी</div>
      </div>
      <div>{{product_category}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Delivery Location</div>
        <div class="label-hi">वितरण स्थान</div>
      </div>
      <div>{{city}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>SCOPE OF WORK / कार्य का दायरा</h3>
    <p><strong>English:</strong> Supply of {{material}} conforming to IS/IEC standards for {{organisation}}.</p>
    <p><strong>हिंदी:</strong> {{organisation}} के लिए IS/IEC मानकों के अनुरूप {{material}} की आपूर्ति।</p>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS / तकनीकी विनिर्देश</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Conductor / कंडक्टर:</strong> Electrolytic Copper, Class 2 stranded (IS 8130)</li>
      <li><strong>Insulation / इन्सुलेशन:</strong> XLPE (Cross-linked Polyethylene)</li>
      <li><strong>Voltage Rating / वोल्टेज रेटिंग:</strong> 1.1 kV / 11 kV grade</li>
      <li><strong>Standards / मानक:</strong> IS 7098, IEC 60502, BIS certified</li>
      <li><strong>Testing / परीक्षण:</strong> NABL accredited lab reports required</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>ELIGIBILITY / पात्रता मानदंड</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Valid BIS license / वैध BIS लाइसेंस</li>
      <li>Minimum 3 similar orders in last 5 years / पिछले 5 वर्षों में न्यूनतम 3 समान आदेश</li>
      <li>ISO 9001:2015 certification / ISO 9001:2015 प्रमाणन</li>
      <li>Average turnover ≥ ₹10 Cr / औसत टर्नओवर ≥ ₹10 करोड़</li>
      <li>Manufacturing capacity ≥ 200 MT/month / विनिर्माण क्षमता ≥ 200 मीट्रिक टन/माह</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>COMMERCIAL TERMS / वाणिज्यिक शर्तें</h3>
    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Earnest Money Deposit</div>
        <div class="label-hi">अर्नेस्ट मनी डिपॉजिट</div>
      </div>
      <div>₹ {{calculateEMD estimated_cost_inr}} (2% of tender value)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Tender Fee</div>
        <div class="label-hi">निविदा शुल्क</div>
      </div>
      <div>₹ 2,950 (Non-refundable / अप्रतिदेय)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Payment Terms</div>
        <div class="label-hi">भुगतान की शर्तें</div>
      </div>
      <div>80% on delivery, 20% after commissioning</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Delivery Period</div>
        <div class="label-hi">डिलीवरी अवधि</div>
      </div>
      <div>60 days from Purchase Order / पर्चेज ऑर्डर से 60 दिन</div>
    </div>

    <div class="bilingual-row">
      <div>
        <div class="label-en">Warranty</div>
        <div class="label-hi">वारंटी</div>
      </div>
      <div>24 months from commissioning / कमीशनिंग से 24 महीने</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h3>CONTACT DETAILS / संपर्क विवरण</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Name / नाम:</strong> {{contact_person}}<br>
      <strong>Email / ईमेल:</strong> {{contact_email}}<br>
      <strong>Phone / फोन:</strong> {{contact_phone}}<br>
      <strong>Office / कार्यालय:</strong> {{organisation}}, {{city}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 25px; text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: #666;">
    Government of India Official Document / भारत सरकार का आधिकारिक दस्तावेज़<br>
    {{tender_id}} | Auto-generated for demonstration
  </div>
</body>
</html>